  53. ‌let run_actions log testenv actions =
  54.   let total = List.length actions in
  55.   let rec run_actions_aux action_number env = function
  56.     | [] -> (Result.pass, env)
  57.     | action::remaining_actions ->
  58.       begin
  59.         Printf.fprintf log "\nRunning action %d/%d (%s)\n%!"
  60.           action_number total (Actions.name action);
  61.         let (result, env') = Actions.run log env action in
  62.         Printf.fprintf log "Action %d/%d (%s) %s\n%!"
  63.           action_number total (Actions.name action)
  64.           (Result.string_of_result result);
  65.         if Result.is_pass result
  66.         then run_actions_aux (action_number+1) env' remaining_actions
  67.         else (result, env')
  68.       end in
  69.   run_actions_aux 1 testenv actions

  71. ‌let run log env test =
  72.   Printf.fprintf log "Running test %s with %d actions\n%!"
  73.     test.test_name
  74.     (List.length test.test_actions);
  75.   run_actions log env test.test_actions
